OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,FThe twin daughters of a man murdered
OL,7,Fby his partner believe he might still
OL,8,Fbe here if more help was available and
OL,9,Fthere was less stigma around male
OL,10,Fvictims coming forward.
OL,12,FAnthony Browne, 54, known as Tony, was
OL,13,Fstabbed in his west Belfast home in
OL,14,FOctober 2022 and later died in
OL,15,Fhospital from his injuries.
OL,17,FHis partner Wiktoria Maksymowicz, from
OL,18,FWoodside Park in Dunmurry, pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to murder and two other
OL,20,Foffences 'aggravated by reason of
OL,21,Finvolving domestic abuse'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
