OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,F"I said, 'Well what happened to my
OL,7,FDad's chest then?'"
OL,9,F"She was like, 'It was the dogs, it
OL,10,Fwas the dogs.'
OL,12,F"My dad's dogs were tiny and I was
OL,13,Flike, 'How was it the dogs?'"
OL,15,F"My daddy jumped in and was like,
OL,16,F'Just leave it, it was the dogs.'
OL,18,F"He just sort of brushed it off,"
OL,19,FShannon said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@SO]qD@AOUtD@AOUuD@]O]wD@AOUzD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@aO]
