OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,FTony is one of many male victims who
OL,7,Fhave suffered abuse at the hands of
OL,8,Fmen and women in intimate partner
OL,9,Frelationships, or within their own
OL,10,Ffamilies.
OL,12,FPSNI statistics show that in the year
OL,13,F2024/ 2025, 33% of domestic abuse
OL,14,Fvictims were male.
OL,16,FFurthermore, the number of male
OL,17,Fvictims at the centre of domestic
OL,18,Fabuse cases has more than doubled over
OL,19,Fthe last 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
