CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780251070
OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,FAdvocacy group Men's Alliance told UTV
OL,7,Fthere is not enough funding or support
OL,8,Fto help men.
OL,10,FChairman Carey Baxter said: "Getting a
OL,11,Frefuge, it could literally be life
OL,12,Fsaving for these men.
OL,14,F"Many, many men over those years have
OL,15,Fleft abusive relationships with
OL,16,Fnowhere to go.
OL,18,F"The Victims Commissioner last year,
OL,19,F2025, they did a mapping exercise for
OL,20,Fservices for men, for male victims of
OL,21,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,26,@rD@]OUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
