PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780251070
OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,F"In the first interview I was involved
OL,7,Fin, the researcher said to me they're
OL,8,Fhaving problems finding organisations
OL,9,Fto put on the map.
OL,11,F"There's minimal services there
OL,12,Fbecause there's minimal funding, and
OL,13,Fthat needs to change."
OL,15,FShannon and Bobbi-Leigh feel that had
OL,16,Fmore support been available, their Dad
OL,17,Fmight still be here.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
