PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780251070
OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,F"If there wasn't a big stigma around
OL,7,Fmen who are abused, I think that he
OL,8,Fwould have felt like it was ok for him
OL,9,Fto speak up about it.
OL,11,F"If there was somewhere where he could
OL,12,Fhave went, obviously they lived
OL,13,Ftogether.
OL,15,F"If there was somewhere he could have
OL,16,Fwent to get away from her, then I
OL,17,Fthink it would have been a different
OL,18,Foutcome.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
