OL,3,C'Had more support been available our
OL,4,CDad might still be here'
OL,6,F"I feel like if there was more support
OL,7,Ffor victims of domestic abuse, that
OL,8,Fthey would be able to find somewhere
OL,9,Fto go, especially men.
OL,11,F"There's no refuges or anything for
OL,12,Fmen. So, if they're trying to escape
OL,13,Fan abusive relationship, they end up
OL,14,Fin their car or on the streets,
OL,15,Fthere's nowhere for them to go".
OL,17,FHelp and support is available for
OL,18,Fvictims and survivors here.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
